Detailed Description

template<class TesPage, class TestFixture>
class gaia::testing::PageUnitTestCase< TesPage, TestFixture >::MockParent

This mock Page represents the "parent" page.

By injecting this, we allow the user to call a few more Page methods, including:

  • gaia::core::Page#getRequestedOrientation()
  • gaia::core::Page#setRequestedOrientation(int)
  • gaia::core::Page#finish()
  • gaia::core::Page#finishPage(int requestCode)
